# SEMrush — Position Tracking (CSV)
# Use for organic Share of Voice, Top-3 keyword count.

column,type,description
date,DATE,YYYY-MM-DD
project_id,STRING,e.g. BE_MAIN
keyword,STRING,Search term
keyword_group,STRING,e.g. Family Dining
dma,STRING,Columbus, etc.
device,STRING,Mobile | Desktop | All
position,NUMBER,Average rank (1–100+)
visibility_percent,NUMBER,Share of voice (0–100)
ranking_url,STRING,URL ranking for this keyword
